      <data key="d0">T of Y</data>
      <data key="d1">function</data>
      <data key="d2">T of Y is a statistical term representing a sufficient statistic for a probability distribution, often used in probabilistic models.&lt;SEP&gt;T of Y is a transformation function that outputs specific K-dimensional vectors based on the input Y value.</data>
