    <node id="Gamma Distribution">
      <data key="d0">Gamma Distribution</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">The Gamma Distribution is a continuous probability distribution often applied in statistics and representing waiting times or intervals.&lt;SEP&gt;The Gamma Distribution is a two-parameter family of continuous probability distributions used in various statistical modeling contexts.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-486f08627d119b0879789e4cf88e8904&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cb276908b4dcc65a416b2c0490f93e3a</data>
