    <node id="Newton's Method">
      <data key="d0">Newton's Method</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">Newton's Method is an algorithm noted for its fast convergence, allowing solutions to achieve higher accuracy with each iteration.&lt;SEP&gt;Newton's Method is an algorithm for finding successively better approximations to the roots of a real-valued function, often used for modeling in machine learning.</data>
